---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About Us — Robles Technologies Corp."
  description="Robles Technologies Corp. bridges world-class IT talent with global opportunity — Smartsheet consulting, AI automation, web development, and more, built on fair partnership and precision execution."
  active=""
>
  <!-- PAGE HERO -->
  <div class="page-hero">
    <div class="page-hero-pat"></div>
    <div class="breadcrumb"><a href="/">Home</a><span>/</span>About</div>
    <span class="sec-tag">Who We Are</span>
    <h1 class="sec-h">Built on one belief:<br>great talent deserves<br>global opportunity</h1>
    <p class="sec-p">Robles Technologies Corp. was founded to bridge world-class IT professionals with businesses that need reliable, high-standard technical execution — without the overhead or friction of traditional offshore models.</p>
  </div>

  <!-- STORY -->
  <section class="about-story sec">
    <div class="about-story-inner">
      <div class="rv">
        <span class="sec-tag">Our Story</span>
        <h2 class="sec-h">From corporate IT to global consulting</h2>
        <p class="sec-p">Robles Technologies Corp. was founded by Kenneth Robles, who transitioned from a corporate IT background to launch an independent consulting firm built around one core principle: that expert technology professionals deserve equitable compensation and real global recognition — and that businesses deserve a tech partner that prioritizes outcomes over output.</p>
        <p class="sec-p" style="margin-top:14px;">We started with Smartsheet consulting — and we're expanding fast. Today, RTC delivers web, app, automation, AI, and integration solutions to clients across industries, with dedicated specialist teams working across each practice area.</p>
        <p class="sec-p" style="margin-top:14px;">Our philosophy is simple: <strong>Redesign, Reinvent, Refocus.</strong> We don't patch broken processes — we rebuild them. We don't just deliver code — we embed with your operations and deliver results.</p>
        <div class="about-mission-grid" style="margin-top:28px;">
          <div class="mission-card"><div class="m-icon"></div><h4>Vision</h4><p>To become a global platform that elevates IT professionals and showcases the Philippines as a premier destination for technology expertise and digital innovation.</p></div>
          <div class="mission-card"><div class="m-icon"></div><h4>Mission</h4><p>To bridge global opportunities with expert talent by delivering innovative technology and consulting solutions — built on trust, precision, and fair partnership.</p></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="rv d1">
        <div class="about-visual-card">
          <h3>RTC by the numbers</h3>
          <p>A growing startup with a global delivery footprint, enterprise-level clients, and a team built for scale.</p>
          <div class="about-stat-row">
            <div class="about-stat-box"><div class="about-stat-num"><span>10+</span></div><div class="about-stat-lbl">Projects Delivered</div></div>
            <div class="about-stat-box"><div class="about-stat-num"><span>F500</span></div><div class="about-stat-lbl">Clients Served</div></div>
            <div class="about-stat-box"><div class="about-stat-num"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="stack-card" style="margin-top:14px;border-radius:17px;padding:30px;">
          <h3>Our current stack</h3>
          <p>Smartsheet is our flagship practice. AI services are live across all tiers. Enterprise platforms expanding soon.</p>
          <div class="chips">
            <span class="chip">Smartsheet</span>
            <span class="chip">Smartsheet API</span>
            <span class="chip">Control Center</span>
            <span class="chip">Data Shuttle</span>
            <span class="chip">Web Development</span>
            <span class="chip">App Development</span>
            <span class="chip">REST APIs</span>
            <span class="chip ai-chip"> AI Automation</span>
            <span class="chip ai-chip"> Custom AI Assistants</span>
            <span class="chip soon">Salesforce ↗</span>
            <span class="chip soon">ServiceNow ↗</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- VALUES -->
  <section class="about-values-full sec" id="values">
    <div class="rv" style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:52px;">
      <span class="sec-tag">What We Stand For</span>
      <h2 class="sec-h">The principles we build everything on</h2>
      <p class="sec-p" style="margin:0 auto;">These aren't aspirational statements. They're the operating principles behind every decision, every hire, and every client engagement we take on.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="values-full-grid">
      <div class="value-full-card rv"><div class="vfc-icon"></div><div class="vfc-title">Fair Compensation</div><p class="vfc-desc">Equitable pay for every team member — always. This is how we attract and keep exceptional talent, and how we ensure the quality of every deliverable we ship.</p></div>
      <div class="value-full-card rv d1"><div class="vfc-icon"></div><div class="vfc-title">Precision Execution</div><p class="vfc-desc">Outcomes-first delivery. Every solution is built to be scalable, reliable, and easy to maintain. We obsess over the details so your team doesn't have to.</p></div>
      <div class="value-full-card rv d2"><div class="vfc-icon"></div><div class="vfc-title">Global Standards</div><p class="vfc-desc">We operate to the same standard as the top-tier global technology firms — without the overhead. World-class execution, accessible pricing.</p></div>
      <div class="value-full-card rv d3"><div class="vfc-icon"></div><div class="vfc-title">True Partnership</div><p class="vfc-desc">We don't fill tickets. We embed with your business, understand your goals, and build solutions that create long-term value — not just short-term deliverables.</p></div>
      <div class="value-full-card rv"><div class="vfc-icon"></div><div class="vfc-title">Transparency First</div><p class="vfc-desc">Fixed-price proposals. No hidden fees. No surprises. You know exactly what you're getting before a single hour of work begins.</p></div>
      <div class="value-full-card rv d1"><div class="vfc-icon"></div><div class="vfc-title">Growth Mindset</div><p class="vfc-desc">We're a startup — and proud of it. We move fast, learn constantly, and build the kind of agile team that can solve problems larger firms can't.</p></div>
      <div class="value-full-card rv d2"><div class="vfc-icon"></div><div class="vfc-title">AI-Forward</div><p class="vfc-desc">AI is central to how we think, build, and advise. We bring practical AI capabilities to every client — not hype, but real solutions that move the needle.</p></div>
      <div class="value-full-card rv d3"><div class="vfc-icon"></div><div class="vfc-title">Community Impact</div><p class="vfc-desc">Every role at RTC creates economic opportunity and global visibility for IT professionals. That impact compounds with every project we deliver.</p></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- MINI STATS BAR -->
  <div class="stats-bar">
    <div class="stats-pat"></div>
    <div class="stat"><div class="stat-n"><span>PH</span></div><div class="stat-l">Philippines-Based</div></div>
    <div class="stat"><div class="stat-n"><span>Multi</span></div><div class="stat-l">Specialist Teams</div></div>
    <div class="stat"><div class="stat-n"><span>Global</span></div><div class="stat-l">Delivery Footprint</div></div>
    <div class="stat"><div class="stat-n"><span>AI</span></div><div class="stat-l">Across All Tiers</div></div>
  </div>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="cta-final">
    <div class="cta-pat"></div>
    <div class="cta-glow"></div>
    <div class="cta-content">
      <span class="sec-tag" style="color:var(--green);">Work With RTC</span>
      <h2 class="sec-h" style="color:var(--white);margin-top:8px;">Ready to build something together?</h2>
      <p class="sec-p" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,.6);margin:0 auto 32px;">Whether you need Smartsheet consulting, AI automation, web development, or a tech team extension — we're ready to help you move faster.</p>
      <div class="cta-actions">
        <a href="mailto:contact@roblestech.net" class="btn btn-white">Discuss Your Project →</a>
        <a href="/services" class="btn btn-ghost">View Services</a>
      </div>
      <p class="cta-hint" style="margin-top:16px;">Or reach us at <a href="mailto:contact@roblestech.net">contact@roblestech.net</a></p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
